        h2.teaser__headline Why do we need Climate Mind?
        .teaser__content
          .teaser__text It can be a real challenge to communicate the realities of climate change to people around you, especially those who have different values and personal interests. 
          .teaser__text Often, people don’t realize actionable solutions already exist that don’t require an overhaul of their personality or beliefs.
        .teaser__subline Our aim is to make conversations about climate change easier.
